owner.name: Switch
owner.description: Take different executions according to the input index. You can click "+" to add more outputs.

owner.name: Flip-Flop
owner.description: Switch between two execution outputs. When this node is triggered for the first time, output A is executed. When it is triggered for the second time, output B is executed. For the third time, output A, and so on.

owner.name: Transit by Time
owner.description: Transition from one value to another according to a certain interpolator within a certain time range. Supported types: Number, Vec2, Vec3, Vec4, and Color.

owner.name: If
owner.description: Take different executions based on conditions.

owner.name: Video Record
owner.description: Execute the next node when recording. By default, in desktop tool preview, it is always recording.

property.value: Execute the next node when recording. By default, in Effect House preview, it is always recording.

owner.name: Equal
owner.description: Compare two inputs and check if they are equal. Supported types: Number, Boolean, Vec2, Vec3, Vec4, Color, and String.
